ytimes.com/1986/05/18/obituaries/astronaut-buried-in-carolina-35-year-mission-is-complete.html | access-date = 2021-11-20 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/05/18/obituaries/astronaut-buried-in-carolina-35-year-mission-is-complete.html }}</ref>，后迁至同城的罗纳德·麦克内尔博士纪念园<ref name="discover_south_caroline">{{cite web | title = Dr. Ronald E. McNair Memorial | publisher = SC Department of Parks, Recreation and Tourism | date = 2021 | url = https://discoversouthcarolina.com/products/26303 | access-date = 2021-11-20 | archive-date = 2021-07-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210701054714/https://discoversouthcarolina.com/products/26303 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="sc_picture_project">{{cite web | title = Ronald E. McNair Memorial Park | publisher = South Carolina Picture Project | date = 2021 | access-date = 2021-11-20 | archive-date = 2021-08-28 | url = https://www.scpictureproject.org/florence-county/ronald-e-mcnair-memorial-park.html | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210828142614/https://www.scpictureproject.org/florence-county/ronald-e-mcnair-memorial-park.html }}</ref>。麦考利芙埋在新罕布什尔州[[康科德_(新罕布什尔州)|康科德]]各各他墓地<ref name="mcauliffe_burial">{{cite web | title = McAuliffe's Grave on a Hillside Overlooks City Where She Taught | publisher = The Los Angeles Times | date = 1986-05-02 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-05-02-mn-3074-story.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210831011210/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-05-02-mn-3074-story.html | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-20 | archive-date = 2021-08-31 }}</ref>，贾维斯火化后骨灰撒入[[太平洋|太平洋]]<ref name="jarvis_ashes">{{cite web | title = Looking back: Greg Jarvis’ dream remembered | publisher = Daily Breeze | date = 2011-01-28 | url = https://www.dailybreeze.com/2011/01/28/looking-back-greg-jarvis-dream-remembered/ | access-date = 2021-11-20 | archive-date = 2021-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210828234153/https://www.dailybreeze.com/2011/01/28/looking-back-greg-jarvis-dream-remembered/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。其他身份不明的遗骸1986年5月20日葬入阿灵顿公墓“挑战者号”航天飞机纪念堂<ref name="arlington_challenger" />。

