美国政界人士在事发后不久质疑[[白宮幕僚長|白宮幕僚長]][[唐纳德·里根|唐纳德·里根]]、[[白宫通讯联络办公室主任|白宫通讯联络办公室主任]][[帕特·布坎南|帕特·布坎南]]等白宫官僚向航空航天局施压，要求在1月28日国情咨文前发射“挑战者号”，铺垫涉及航天飞机的总统演说<ref name="nyt_sotu">{{cite web | last = Boyd | first = Gerald M. | title = White House Finds no Pressure to Launch | publisher = The New York Times | date = 1986-04-04 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-08-30 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/04/04/us/white-house-finds-no-pressure-to-launch.html | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830020010/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/04/04/us/white-house-finds-no-pressure-to-launch.html }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web | url = https://apnews.com/00a395472559b3afcd22de473da2e65f | title = NASA Suggested Reagan Hail Challenger Mission in State of Union | last = Hunt | first = Terence | publisher = Associated Press | access-date = 2021-11-21 | date = 1986-03-13 | archive-date = 2021-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830132858/https://apnews.com/00a395472559b3afcd22de473da2e65f | dead-url = no }}</ref>。白宫同年3月公布原版国情咨文稿件副本，表明里根原计划邀请他人前往现场，演说简要提及此人设计并计划在航天飞机开展的[[X射线|X射线]]实验，此外没有进一步谈论“挑战者号”发射<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite book | dead-url = no | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=Ith7DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA283&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | title = Ronald Reagan and the Space Frontier | last = Logsdon | first = John M. | date = 2018-11-26 | publisher = Springer | isbn = 978-3-319-98962-4 | page = 283 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-02-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204125449/https://books.google.com/books?id=Ith7DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA283}}</ref>。总统在推迟到2月4日的国情咨文谈到遇难乘组，把涉及X射线实验的语句改为说明“挑战者号”“发射后失敗”<ref name="1986_sotu_transcript">{{cite web | url = https://www.reaganlibrary.gov/archives/speech/address-joint-session-congress-state-union-1986 | title = Address Before a Joint Session of Congress on the State of the Union – 1986 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | date = 1986-02-04 | last = Reagan | first = Ronald | au