=== 传媒报道 ===
[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]向全国报道“挑战者号”发射及失事<ref name="cnn_coverage">{{cite web | last = Escobedo | first = Tricia | title = When a national disaster unfolded live in 1986 | publisher = CNN | date = 2016-03-31 | url = https://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/31/us/80s-cnn-challenger-coverage/index.html | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211101044531/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/31/us/80s-cnn-challenger-coverage/index.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。为宣传麦考利芙所属太空教师计划，航空航天局安排全美大量儿童在学校观看发射实况<ref name="cnn_coverage" /><ref name="children">{{cite journal | last = Wright | first = John C. | author2 = Dale Kunkel | author3 = Marites Pinon | author4 = Aletha C. Huston | title = How Children Reacted to Televised Coverage of the Space Shuttle Disaster | journal = Journal of Communication | publisher = International Communication Association | volume = 39 | issue = 2 | page = 27 | date = Spring 1989 | doi = 10.1111/j.1460-2466.1989.tb01027.x}}</ref>。传媒对事故兴趣激增，发射当天肯尼迪航天中心共有535名记者，三天后增至1467人<ref name="harwood 6">{{cite news | last = Harwood | first = William | title = Voyage into History; Chapter Six: The Reaction | year = 1986 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/network/news/space/51Lchap6reaction.html | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20060504192714/http://www.cbsnews.com/network/news/space/51Lchap6reaction.html | archive-date = 2006-05-04 | accessdate = 2007-05-06 }}</ref>。事故发生后，航空航天局因未安排关键人员向媒体公布消息受批评<ref>{{cite news | last = Reinhold | first = Robert | title = The Shuttle Explosion; At Mission Control, Silence and Grief Fill a Day Of Horror Long Dreaded | publisher = The New York Times | access-date = 2021-11-21 | date = 1986-01-29 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/01/29/us/shuttle-explosion-mission-control-silence-grief-fill-day-horror-long-dreaded.html | archive-date = 2021-10-28 | page = A8 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211028055031/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/01/29/us/shuttle-explosion-mission-control-silence-grief-fill-day-horror-long-dreaded.html }}</ref>。得不到确切信息的媒体一度发表文章，推断爆炸是外储箱引起<ref name="harwood 6" /><ref name="nytimes_et">{{cite web | last = Browne | first = Malcolm W. | title = How could it happen? Fuel Tank Leak Feared | publisher = The New York Times | date = 1986-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210830092242/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/01/29/us/how-could-it-happen-fuel-tank-leak-feared.html | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/01/29/us/how-could-it-happen-fuel-tank-leak-feared.html | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-08-30 | dead-url = no | page = A1 }}</ref>。事发后近四分之一个世纪里，只有有线电视新闻网在发射场范围拍下的“挑战者号”发射与失事过程為公眾所知，之后才有其他专业或业余拍摄片段陆续公布<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210629030321/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/space-shuttle-challenger-home-video_n_4677745 | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/space-shuttle-challenger-home-video_n_4677745 | title = Challenger Disaster Home Video Surfaces After 28 Years | date = 2014-01-28 | first = Timothy | last = Stevonec | publisher = The Huffington Post | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-06-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.huffpost.com/entry/new-challenger-video-space-shuttle-footage_n_1463495 | title = New Challenger Video: Rare Footage Of 1986 Disaster Uncovered | date = 2012-05-01 | first = Timothy | last = Stevonec | publisher = The Huffington Post | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928223654/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/new-challenger-video-space-shuttle-footage_n_1463495 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.theguardian.com/science/2010/feb/04/challenger-space-shuttle-video-discovered | title = Challenger space shuttle disaster amateur video discovered | first = Richard | last = Luscombe | date = 2010-02-04 | publisher = The Guardian | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210712074115/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2010/feb/04/challenger-space-shuttle-video-discovered | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 工程案例研究 ===
“挑战者号”事故是[[安全工程|安全工程]]、[[吹哨人|检举]]伦理、传播与集体决策、[[團體迷思|團體迷思]]风险等领域的研究案例<ref name="boisjoly_ethics_paper">{{cite journal | last1 = Boisjoly | first1 = Russell P. | last2 = Curtis | first2 = Ellen Foster | last3 = Mellican | first3 = Eugene | title = Roger Boisjoly and the Challenger Disaster: The Ethical Dimensions | date = 1989-04 | url = https://www.jstor.org/stable/25071892 | journal = Journal of Business Ethics | publisher = Springer | volume = 8 | issue = 4 | pages = 217–230 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-08-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210831110022/https://www.jstor.org/stable/25071892 | dead-url = no | jstor = 25071892 }}</ref>。博伊斯乔与麦克唐纳为倡导职业场所决策责任和工程道德发声<ref name="berkes20120206" /><ref name="mcdonald_npr_obit">{{cite web | last = Berkes | first = Howard | title = Remembering Allan McDonald: He Refused To Approve Challenger Launch, Exposed Cover-Up | work = Obituaries | archive-date = 2021-11-19 | url = https://www.npr.org/2021/03/07/974534021/remembering-allan-mcdonald-he-refused-to-approve-challenger-launch-exposed-cover | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = National Public Radio | date = 2021-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211119221415/https://www.npr.org/2021/03/07/974534021/remembering-allan-mcdonald-he-refused-to-approve-challenger-launch-exposed-cover | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[信息设计|信息设计师]][[爱德华·塔夫特|爱德华·塔夫特]]主张，工程人员沟通不力且解释太过复杂是“挑战者号”惨剧的根本原因，只要证明发射环境气温和O形环侵蚀程度密切关联就足以说明寒冷天气发射的潜在风险。博伊斯乔提出质疑，认为实际情况并不像塔夫特所言那么简单，没那么容易找足数据证明。<ref name="WadeNAE96">{{cite journal | last1 = Robison | first1 = Wade | last2 = Boisjoly | first2 = Roger | last3 = Hoeker | first3 = David | last4 = Young | first4 = Stefan | year = 2002 | title = Representation and Misrepresentation: Tufte and the Morton Thiokol Engineers on the Challenger | journal = Science and Engineering Ethics | volume = 8 | issue = 1 | pages = 59–81 | url = https://people.rit.edu/wlrgsh/FINRobison.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | doi = 10.1007/s11948-002-0033-2 | pmid = 11840958 | s2cid = 19219936 | archive-date = 2021-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211011234327/https://people.rit.edu/wlrgsh/FINRobison.pdf }}</ref>

== 罗杰斯委员会 ==
{{Main|罗杰斯委员会}}
“挑战者号”航天飞机事故调查总统委员会2月6日成立，因主席[[威廉·P·罗杰斯|威廉·P·罗杰斯]]又称罗杰斯委员会<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|206}}，其他委员包括副主席[[尼尔·阿姆斯特朗|尼尔·阿姆斯特朗]]、[[大卫·坎皮恩·艾奇逊|大卫·坎皮恩·艾奇逊]]、[[尤金·科弗特|尤金·科弗特]]、[[理查德·費曼|理查德·費曼]]、罗伯特·霍茨、[[唐纳德·库蒂纳|唐纳德·库蒂纳]]、[[萨莉·莱德|萨莉·莱德]]、罗伯特·鲁梅尔、[[乔·萨特|乔·萨特]]、[[小亚瑟·沃克|亚瑟·沃克]]、艾伯特·惠伦、[[查克·葉格|查克·葉格]]<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|iii-iv}}。

委员会召开听证会讨论航空航天局事故调查、航天飞机项目、赛奥科不顾O形环安全隐患建议发射等问题。2月15日，罗杰斯声明委员会调整职能独立调查“挑战者号”事故以免受航空航天局内部流程和问题影响。委员会设立四个调查组研究失事任务各方面：库蒂纳领导事故分析组根据打捞作业和测试数据判断事故确切原因；萨特为首的开发生产组调查航天飞机各部件承包商及其与航空航天局的交流互动；艾奇逊带领发射前活动组关注在肯尼迪航天中心开展的最终装配过程和发射前活动；莱德带头任务规划与行动组审视任务开发前的规划过程，以及乘组安全潜在问题和航空航天局是否受到压力坚持发射日程。委员会在四个月间访谈160余人，举行至少35场调查会议，调查涉事航空航天局工作人员、承包商雇员、支持人员六千余人<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|206−208}}，最后在6月6日公布报告<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|iii-iv}}。
[[File:Rogers_Commission_members_arrive_at_Kennedy_Space_Center.jpg|thumb]]成员抵达[[肯尼迪航天中心|肯尼迪航天中心]]]]

委员会认定事故是由炽热气体穿过右侧固体助推器现场安装接头的O形环引发，没有证据表明还有其他因素<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|71}}。报告指出，安装接头材料对温度和负载变化非常敏感，说明初使设计考虑不周，存在重大缺陷<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|73}}。文中批评航空航天局和赛奥科对接头潜在危险的证据视而不见，航空航天局根本没有评估潜在影响就接受O形环侵蚀风险<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|149}}，机构对安全问题的态度和管理结构都不足以合理汇报、分析、防范飞行问题<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|162}}。报告进一步阐明，航空航天局急于提升任务频率，由此构成的压力对各任务培训量、质量控制、维修作业不利<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|177}}。

委员会提出大量旨在提升航天飞机项目安全程度的建议，如重新设计固体助推器接头，防止气体经过O形环；重组航天飞机项目管理层，防止项目主管受到最后期限的压力而危及安全，而且管理层应有航天员介入，以期更加妥善地解决乘组安全问题。报告提出设立直接向航空航天局长汇报的安全办公室，监督航空航天局项目所有影响安全、可靠程度、质量保证职能的事务。此外，委员会针对轨道器整体安全与维护需求建议增加受控滑翔时乘组逃生的手段。<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|198–200}}

[[诺贝尔物理学奖|诺贝尔物理学奖]]得主费曼在2月11日电视转播的听证会上用冷水和橡胶证明低温会令橡胶失去弹力，引起传媒关注。费曼主张在委员会报告更加严厉地批评航空航天局，多次与罗杰斯意见相左，还以拒绝签字威胁要求报告纳入他对航天飞机可靠程度的个人见解，这些内容最后写入附录F。<ref name="feynman_nyt">{{cite web | last = Boffrey | first = Philip M. | title = Amid Disputes, Shuttle Panel Finally Forged an Agreement | publisher = The New York Times | date = 1986-06-07 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-08-31 | dead-url = no | page = 11 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/06/07/us/amid-disputes-shuttle-panel-finally-forged-an-agreement.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210831110019/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/06/07/us/amid-disputes-shuttle-panel-finally-forged-an-agreement.html }}</ref><ref name="appendixF">{{cite book | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | url = https://history.nasa.gov/rogersrep/v2appf.htm | title = Report of the Presidential Commission on the Space Shuttle Challenger Accident | publisher = [[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]] | volume = 2 | location = Appendix F | date = 1986-06-06 | chapter = Personal Observations on Reliability of Shuttle | last = Feynman | first = R.P. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211116215224/https://history.nasa.gov/rogersrep/v2appf.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>费曼执笔的附录称赞航天飞机开发在工程和软件领域成就显著，但除固体助推器外，航空电子设备、航天飞机主发动机等许多部件都比航空航天局原本预计的更危险、更容易诱发事故<ref name="appendixF" /><ref name="feynman_physics_today">{{cite web | last = Feynman | first = Richard P. | author-link = 理查德·費曼 | title = An Outsider's Inside View of the Challenger Inquiry | publisher = Physics Today | date = 1988-02 | format = PDF | url = https://authors.library.caltech.edu/51304/1/challenger.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211008130601/https://authors.library.caltech.edu/51304/1/challenger.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 美国众议院委员会报告 ===
[[美国众议院科技委员会|美国众议院科技委员会]]调查事故并在10月29日公布报告<ref name="House Committee">{{cite web | author = U.S House Committee on Science and Technology | title = Investigation of the Challenger Accident; Report of the Committee on Science and Technology, House of Representatives | publisher = US Government Printing Office | date = 1986-10-29 | url = https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/GPO-CRPT-99hrpt1016/pdf/GPO-CRPT-99hrpt1016.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-06 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211006084009/https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/GPO-CRPT-99hrpt1016/pdf/GPO-CRPT-99hrpt1016.pdf }}</ref>{{rp|i}}。该委员会有权决定是否向航天飞机项目拨款，调查期间还检视罗杰斯委员会的报告。科技委员会认可罗杰斯委员会对事故由固体助推器安装接头故障引发、航空航天局与赛奥科对多番警示和固体助推器风险置若罔闻的判断，进而强调其他航天飞机部件也存在安全问题，建议审查所有关键功能的风险管理。<ref name="House Committee" />{{rp|2–5}}

== 航空航天局响应 ==
=== 重新设计固体助推器 ===
航空航天局根据罗杰斯委员会报告在独立监督组督导下重新设计固体助推器，后起名再设计固体火箭发动机<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|198}}<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-101}}<ref name="implementation report">{{cite web | title = Report to the President: Actions to Implement the Recommendations of the Presidential Commission on the Space Shuttle Challenger Accident | publisher = NASA | date = 1986-07-14 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | url = https://history.nasa.gov/rogersrep/actions.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211116221458/https://history.nasa.gov/rogersrep/actions.pdf }}</ref>。新设计接头在与U形夹内壁结合的柄脚上新增捕获功能，能把“挑战者号”事故时发生的节点旋转几率降至一成五；捕获功能件与U形夹间空隙另以O形环密封。如果还是发生节点旋转降低U形夹内壁任何一边的密封效果，另一边的效果就会增强。接头内新增加热器，确保O形环温度一致且不会太低。<ref name="mcdonald" />{{rp|429–430}}再设计固体火箭发动机1987年8月30日首度测试，次年四月和八月测试时有意令炽热气体通过接头处，以便工程人员评估新接头能够防止节点旋转。测试通过后，新设计获许装上航天飞机。<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-101}}

=== 航天飞机改装 ===
除固体助推器外，航空航天局还提升航天飞机其他部件的安全标准，更新关键项目清单和航天飞机主发动机故障模式外，施行18项硬件调整。主发动机最大推力限制在104%，只有中止任务时才能升至109%。<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|II-172}}起落架经过变更，提升航天飞机降落时的转向和驾驶功能<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-104}}。航空航天局加入乘组逃生功能，航天员在侧舱门弹出后把滑杆伸出轨道器，从滑杆离开再打开[[降落伞|降落伞]]以免直接跳出时遭轨道器撞击。轨道器软件更新后，即便乘组全部逃生也能维持稳定飞行。<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-103}}上述逃生手段不足以在“挑战者号”事故时挽救乘组生命，而是针对另一起航天飞机紧急情况新增<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-102}}。

=== 安全与任务保证办公室 ===
航空航天局设立安全与任务保证办公室，并按罗杰斯委员会要求由直接向局长汇报的副局长负责<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|199}}<ref name="recommendation_7" /><ref name="nasa_implementation">{{cite web | title = NASA's Actions to Implement the Rogers Commission Recommendations after the Challenger Accident | publisher = NASA | date = 2000-07-18 | url = https://www.hq.nasa.gov/office/pao/History/actions.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210305171248/https://www.hq.nasa.gov/office/pao/History/actions.html | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-03-05 }}</ref>。“挑战者号”飞行指导格林担任新办公室安全部主任<ref name="jh-greene-bio">{{cite web | title = Jay H. Greene | work = Oral History Project | publisher = NASA | date = 2004-07-12 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | url = https://historycollection.jsc.nasa.gov/JSCHistoryPortal/history/oral_histories/GreeneJH/GreeneJH_Bio.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211025130516/https://historycollection.jsc.nasa.gov/JSCHistoryPortal/history/oral_histories/GreeneJH/GreeneJH_Bio.pdf }}</ref>。2003年[[哥伦比亚号航天飞机灾难|“哥伦比亚号”航天飞机失事]]后，[[哥伦比亚号事故调查委员会|哥伦比亚号事故调查委员会]]认定航空航天局设立的安全与任务保证办公室在安全监督方面仍然不够独立<ref name="caib_report">{{cite journal | last1 = Gehman | first1 = Harold | last2 = Barry | first2 = John | last3 = Deal | first3 = Duane | last4 = Hallock | first4 = James | last5 = Hess | first5 = Kenneth | last6 = Hubbard | first6 = G. Scott | last7 = Logsdon | first7 = John | last8 = Logsdon | first8 = John | author-link8 = 道格拉斯·奥谢罗夫 | last9 = Ride | first9 = Sally | last10 = Tetrault | first10 = Roger | last11 = Turcotte | first11 = Stephen | last12 = Wallace | first12 = Steven | last13 = Widnall | first13 = Sheila | title = Report of Columbia Accident Investigation Board | volume = 1 | publisher = NASA | date = 2003-08-26 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-05 | dead-url = no | format = PDF | url = http://s3.amazonaws.com/akamai.netstorage/anon.nasa-global/CAIB/CAIB_lowres_full.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211005003854/http://s3.amazonaws.com/akamai.netstorage/anon.nasa-global/CAIB/CAIB_lowres_full.pdf }}</ref>{{rp|178}}，委员会进一步指出，航空航天局的管理文化对安全重视不够，进而导致“挑战者号”与“哥伦比亚号”惨剧<ref name="caib_report" />{{rp|195}}。

=== 太空教师计划 ===
麦考利芙所在的太空教师计划因“挑战者号”失事于1990年取消，航空航天局1998年提出教育家航天员计划，与太空教师计划的主要区别在于新计划旨在把教师训练成专业航天员并授受任务专家培训，参与老计划的教师只需临时充当有效载荷专家，任务完成后回课堂教学。[[芭芭拉·摩根|芭芭拉·摩根]]是麦考利芙的替补，1998年入选[[第17组宇航员|第17组宇航员]]并随[[STS-118|STS-118]]任务飞上蓝天。<ref name="jenkins2016" />{{rp|III-116}}

=== 航天飞机复飞 ===
{{Further2|[[美國太空梭計劃|美國太空梭計劃]]|[[STS-26|STS-26]]}}
罗杰斯委员会批评航空航天局每年发射24次航天飞机的目标不切实际，产生不必要的发射压力<ref name="rogers_com" />{{rp|165}}。里根总统1986年8月批准新建轨道器取代“挑战者号”，后起名“[[奮進號太空梭|奋进号]]”。新轨道器次年开建，1990年完成，1992年5月首飞执行[[STS-49|STS-49]]任务。<ref name="endeavour_nasa">{{cite web | last = Ryba | first = Jeanne | title = Space Shuttle Overview: Endeavour (OV-105) | publisher = NASA | date = 2013-04-12 | url = https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/shuttleoperations/orbiters/endeavour-info.html | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211116233625/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/shuttleoperations/orbiters/endeavour-info.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>里根还宣布今后商务[[人造衛星|卫星]]以商用[[一次性使用运载系统|一次运载火箭]]发射，不再由航天飞机部署<ref name="reagan_latimes">{{cite web | last = Abramson | first = Rudy | title = Reagan Orders Shuttle, Limits NASA Mission | publisher = [[洛杉磯時報|The Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1986-08-16 | archive-date = 2021-09-02 | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-08-16-mn-7268-story.html | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210902120601/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-08-16-mn-7268-story.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="endeavour_order">{{cite web | last = Ryba | first = Jeanne | title = Space Shuttle Overview: Endeavour (OV-105) | publisher = NASA | date = 2013-04-12 | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-16 | url = https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/shuttleoperations/orbiters/endeavour-info.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211116233625/https://www.nasa.gov/centers/kennedy/shuttleoperations/orbiters/endeavour-info.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。商务卫星改用一次运载火箭发射后，航空航天局就不需再为满足客户需要启动航天飞机载人任务<ref name="wilford_shuttle">{{cite web | last = Wilford | first = John Noble | title = Reagan is reported near decision to approve a new Space Shuttle | publisher = The New York times | date = 1986-05-25 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1986/05/25/us/reagan-is-reported-near-decision-to-approve-a-new-space-shuttle.html | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-10 | page = 11 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211110125348/https://www.nytimes.com/1986/05/25/us/reagan-is-reported-near-decision-to-approve-a-new-space-shuttle.html }}</ref>。

“挑战者”失事后，航天飞机停飞两年零八个月等待调查、再设计、重组。1988年9月29日，[[發現號太空梭|發現號太空梭]]装载五名资深航天员从39B号发射台升空，执行[[STS-26|STS-26]]任务。<ref>{{cite web | first = John A. | last = Logsdon | url = https://history.nasa.gov/SP-4219/Chapter15.html | publisher = NASA | title = Return to Flight: Richard H. Truly and the Recovery from the Challenger Accident | access-date = 2021-11-21 | date = 1998 | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224180805/https://history.nasa.gov/SP-4219/Chapter15.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>机上载有跟踪和数据中继卫星[[TDRS-3|TDRS-3]]，用于补充随“挑战者号”损失的卫星。发射采用重新设计的助推器，乘组在上升和再入期间身着压力航天服。任务顺利完成后航天飞机复飞。<ref name="sts26">{{cite web | last = Mars | first = Kelli | title = 30 Years Ago: STS-26 Returns Shuttle to Flight | publisher = NASA | date = 2018-09-28 | url = https://www.nasa.gov/feature/30-years-ago-sts-26-returns-shuttle-to-flight/ | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-05-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210526152213/https://www.nasa.gov/feature/30-years-ago-sts-26-returns-shuttle-to-flight/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

