planetcenter.net/iau/ECS/MPCArchive/1986/MPC_19860326.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210727220035/https://minorplanetcenter.net/iau/ECS/MPCArchive/1986/MPC_19860326.pdf | access-date = 2021-11-21 | date = 1986-03-26 | archive-date = 2021-07-27 | dead-url = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。1988年，[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]用七人姓氏为[[月球|月球]]背面[[阿波罗环形山|阿波罗盆地]]的七个陨石坑起名<ref name="jarvis_astro">{{cite web | url = https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/2808 | title = Jarvis | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = United States Geological Survey | date = 2010-10-18 | archive-date = 2021-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210624222417/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/2808 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="mcauliffe_astro">{{cite web | url = https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3777 | title = McAuliffe | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = United States Geological Survey | date = 2010-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210625152452/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3777 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-06-25 }}</ref><ref name="mcnair_astro">{{cite web | url = https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3785 | title = McNair | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = United States Geological Survey | date = 2010-10-18 | archive-date = 2021-08-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210831201618/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/3785 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="onizuka_astro">{{cite web | url = https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/4468 | title = Onizuka | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = United States Geological Survey | date = 2010-10-18 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127013624/https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/4468 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="resnik_astro">{{cite web | url = https://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5002 | title = Resnik | access-date = 2021-11-21 | publisher = United States Geological Survey