nia) | publisher = Astronaut Ellison S. Onizuka Memorial | date = 2021 | url = https://onizukamemorial.org/space-shuttle-challenger-and-monument | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210828142617/https://onizukamemorial.org/space-shuttle-challenger-and-monument | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-08-28 }}</ref>。[[桑格雷·德克里斯托山脉|桑格雷·德克里斯托山脉]]高峰更名[[挑战者峰|挑战者峰]]纪念失事任务<ref name=GNIS>{{cite gnis|id=196427|name=Challenger Point|entry-date=1992-08-31 | access-date = 2021-07-15}}</ref>。新罕布什尔州康科德的科学博物馆和天文馆[[麦考利芙－谢泼德发现中心|麦考利芙－谢泼德发现中心]]名称旨在纪念当地高中教师麦考利芙和首位美国太空人[[艾伦·谢泼德|艾伦·谢泼德]]<ref name="mcauliffe-shepard">{{cite web | title = About | publisher = McAuliffe-Shepard Discovery Center | date = 2021 | url = https://www.starhop.com/about | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211026090254/https://www.starhop.com/about | dead-url = no }}</ref>。“挑战者号”遇难乘组家属成立[[非營利組織|非营利]]教育组织[[挑战者号太空教育科学中心|挑战者号太空教育科学中心]]<ref name="challenger_center">{{cite web | title = About Us | publisher = Challenger Center for Space Science Education | date = 2019 | url = https://www.challenger.org/who-we-are/#about_us | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211114035405/https://www.challenger.org/who-we-are/#about_us | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

