ure To Communicate | publisher = Forbes | date = 2019-01-28 | url = https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnbaldoni/2019/01/28/the-challenger-disaster-a-dramatic-lesson-in-the-failure-to-communicate/ | access-date = 2021-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211031222652/https://www.forbes.com/sites/johnbaldoni/2019/01/28/the-challenger-disaster-a-dramatic-lesson-in-the-failure-to-communicate/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

